      "module_path": "tddd",
      "docs": "Secondary port that persists Reality View (baseline graph) mermaid markdown files. write_overview writes <layer>-graph-d1/index.md; write_cluster writes <layer>-graph-d2/<cluster_key>.md. Symmetric to ContractMapWriter. Implementations must write atomically and refuse to follow symlinks below the caller-supplied trust root. (IN-02 / IN-19 / AC-02 / CN-03)",
